<h1>友链</h1>
<div class="link-grid">
<% if (site.data.link) { site.data.link.forEach(function(link) { %>
<div class="link-card">
  <img src="<%= link.avatar %>" alt="<%= link.name %>的头像" loading="lazy">
  <div class="link-card-body">
    <a href="<%= link.url %>" target="_blank" rel="noopener noreferrer"><%= link.name %></a>
    <div class="link-desc"><%= link.desc %></div>
    <% if (link.note) { %>
    <span class="link-note"><%= link.note %></span>
    <% } %>
  </div>
</div>
<% }); } %>
</div>
<hr>
<section class="link-section">
  <h2>交换友链</h2>
  <p>如果你想与本博客交换友链，请在下方填写你的博客信息，我会尽快添加</p>
  <p><strong>请确保你也添加了本博客的链接后再申请</strong></p>
  <form class="link-form">
    <div class="form-group">
      <label for="link-name">博客名称</label>
      <input type="text" id="link-name" name="name" required placeholder="你的博客名称" />
    </div>
    <div class="form-group">
      <label for="link-url">博客地址</label>
      <input type="url" id="link-url" name="url" required placeholder="https://example.com" />
    </div>
    <div class="form-group">
      <label for="link-avatar">头像链接</label>
      <input type="url" id="link-avatar" name="avatar" required placeholder="https://example.com/avatar.jpg" />
    </div>
    <div class="form-group">
      <label for="link-desc">博客描述</label>
      <input type="text" id="link-desc" name="desc" required placeholder="一句话介绍你的博客" />
    </div>
    <button type="submit">生成友链代码</button>
  </form>
  <div id="link-result"></div>
</section>
<script src="/js/link.js"></script>
<hr>
<h2>本站信息</h2>
<div class="card-list">
<div class="card">
  <div class="card-meta"><span>名称：xf_blog</span></div>
  <div class="card-meta"><span>链接：<a href="https://xfcnl.github.io">https://xfcnl.github.io</a></span></div>
  <div class="card-meta"><span>头像：<a href="https://github.com/xfcnl/xfcnl.github.io/blob/main/image/MEITU_20260128_220225596.jpg?raw=true">GitHub 直链</a></span></div>
  <div class="card-meta"><span>签名：立志用 cloudflare workers，GitHub pages 和 vercel 做出整个互联网的 up（虽然不会成功</span></div>
</div>
</div>
<hr>
